HEADWORD: Transpalatine
<hw>Trans*pal"a*tine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>trans-</ets> + <ets>palatine</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
